description: This course takes the viewer step-by-step through the multivariate analysis of variance (MANOVA) statistical procedure in SPSS . Several different examples of MANOVA are covered, including MANOVA with 2 groups, MANOVA with 3 groups, post hoc tests, and a two-way MANOVA. Each video illustrates step by step how to both run a MANOVA in SPSS and interpret the results. Written results of each MANOVA are also provided. Designed by an award-winning university statistics instructor with a focus on simple and accurate (step by step) explanations of the material.
title: Statistics / Data Analysis in SPSS: MANOVA
